richTextEditor1.setValue("<p>Hi Retool,</p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://home.admin.retool.dev\" target=\"_blank\">Retool Home</a> is a new company-wide people, team, and culture directory. ICYM our launch at All Hands last week, <strong>Retool Home is available for all employees and includes the following:</strong></p><ul><li>People directory</li><li>Team directory</li><li>Personalized profiles for all employees</li><li>Announcements</li><li>Our new Decision Log</li><li>Badges</li><li>And a new home for Big Ups and Shipped</li></ul><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;\">We have loads more features planned, so stay tuned for an update at our December all hands. And please keep the feedback coming!</span></p><p>You can access Retool Home from re/home or <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://home.admin.retool.dev\" target=\"_blank\">https://home.admin.retool.dev</a> using Okta SSO.</p><p><strong>My asks from you:</strong></p><ol><li>Please sign up for Retool Home</li><li>Update your profile (you can access it from the top-right avatar user menu dropdown)</li><li>If you are a team lead, also update your team page with a description and links to your Slack, Confluence, and Linear.</li><li>Start using Retool Home for ships, big ups, announcements, and more.</li><li>If you see any bugs or incorrect team data - please ping me or submit feedback directly in Retool Home.</li></ol><p><strong>And finally, massive shout-outs the following folks for helping make Retool Home possible:</strong></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">David &amp; the staff team for pushing the project forward, providing feedback, and buying into our new decision log.</span></li><li>Chris S, JD, Willa, and Gabie from the Brand Design team for some sweet badge designs and an updated logo variation.</li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Adrian, Rose, and Celine from the people team for helping me standardize and collect team info.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">IT for helping get Okta set up so everyone has access. </span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Kent for design magic including a new theme. </span></li><li>Julie for deployed performance help to improve some of the page load times (still work to do here!)</li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">The Governance team for making this possible in a space in admin</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">JJZ, Ming, Darya, Isbella, Amanda, Matt C and the rest of the Platform team working on multipage! </span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Aimee for helping integrate our KPIs and linking to the core metrics dashboard&nbsp;</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Mike Y for helping put together the decision log and helping backfill&nbsp;decisions from Staff.</span></li></ul><p>Thanks for all of the feedback since launch! Now, back to fixing all of those bugs you reported and add those features you requested. 🫡</p>")","playgroundQueryUuid","","playgroundQueryId",null,"error",null,"workflowRunBodyType","raw","privateParams",["^D",[]],"workflowBlockUuid",null,"queryRunOnSelectorUpdate",false,"runWhenPageLoadsDelay","","data",null,"importedQueryInputs",["^57",[]],"_additionalScope",["^D",[]],"isImported",false,"showSuccessToaster",false,"cacheKeyTtl","","requestSentTimestamp",null,"metadata",null,"workflowActionType",null,"queryRunTime",null,"changesetObject","","offlineOptimisticResponse",null,"errorTransformer","return data.error","finished",null,"confirmationMessage",null,"isFetching",false,"changeset","","rawData",null,"queryTriggerDelay","0","resourceTypeOverride",null,"watchedParams",["^D",[]],"enableErrorTransformer",false,"isHidden",false,"showLatestVersionUpdatedWarning",false,"timestamp",0,"importedQueryDefaults",["^57",[]],"enableTransformer",false,"showUpdateSetValueDynamicallyTo